Load libraries and QCFiltered dataset

#load library
library(Seurat)
library(RColorBrewer)

#Set ggplot theme
theme_set(theme_classic())
# Load the full annotated dataset
Allcells.data <- readRDS("./Clustered.cells.RDS")

Plot the different features

FeaturePlot(object = Allcells.data,
            features.plot = "BP_signature1",
            cols.use = rev(brewer.pal(10,"Spectral")),
            reduction.use = "spring",
            no.legend = T,
            overlay = F,
            dark.theme = F
            )

FeaturePlot(object = Allcells.data,
            features.plot = c("Top2a", "Eomes", "Mki67", "Btg2", "Cdk1", "Neurog2", "Aurka"),
            cols.use = c("grey90", brewer.pal(9,"YlGnBu")),
            reduction.use = "spring",
            no.legend = T,
            overlay = F,
            dark.theme = F)
